    public class OfferListActivity
extends android.support.v7.app.AppCompatActivity
implements com.android.volley.Response.Listener<org.json.JSONObject>, com.android.volley.Response.ErrorListener
    Renders a list of offers available in the chosen SubCategory . An OfferItem contains data about a dish such as name, price, selling restaurant and contact info for the restaurant.
